        <section class="product-three-points-container product-secure-three-points-container clearfix" style="display: none;">
            <div class="container" style="max-width:100% !important">

                <ul>

                    

                        <li class="animate-it fadeInLeft" data-delay="100" style="background-image:url(https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1.png)">High Fixed Returns<br/>
                            <div style="margin-top:8px"><span>Build your wealth with a personalised, diversified portfolio with expert advice.</span></div>
                        </li>


                    

                        <li class="animate-it fadeInLeft" data-delay="200" style="background-image:url(https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/2.png)">Outperforming Market<br/>
                            <div style="margin-top:8px"><span>Earn returns that are greater than the market average with minimal risk and a broader risk profile, we've proudly been beating the market since 2016 for our clients.</span></div>
                        </li>


                    

                        <li class="animate-it fadeInLeft" data-delay="300" style="background-image:url(https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3.png)">Profit Sharing Model<br/>
                            <div style="margin-top:8px"><span>Operating under a model of profit sharing, we make money when our investors make money and our success depends on your success.</span></div>
                        </li>


                                    </ul>
                
