                                    <img src="https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/themes/twentytwenty-child/assets/images/news-blank-2.png" alt="Strait of Hormuz Market Impact and Investor Strategy"  style="background-image: url('https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/ARTICLE-IMAGE-851x553.jpg');">
                                                            </div>
                            <div class="content ">
                                <span class="tag">Insight</span>
                                <div class="v-align">
                                    <div class="tooltip">
                                        <h3>Strait of Hormuz Market Impact and Investor Strategy</h3>

                                        <span class="tooltiptext">
												<span>March has been one of the most geopolitically sensitive periods markets have faced in recent years. Escalating tensions between the United States, Israel and Iran have created a volatile environment not only for the Middle East but for global financial markets.</span>
											</span>

                                    </div>
                                                                        <span class="date">March 26, 2026</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </article>
                    <div class="clr"></div>                    
                    <article class="news horizontal">
                        <a href="https://aixfincon.com/yolo-fomo-momo/">
                            <div class="thumbnail animate-it" data-delay="100">
                                
                                    <img src="https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/themes/twentytwenty-child/assets/images/news-blank-3.png" alt="YOLO → FOMO → MOMO"  style="background-image: url('https://aixfincon.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/marcel-strauss-yP7uoJdxkjg-unsplash-851x553.jpg');">
                                                            </div>
                            <div class="content ">
